{"about_the_game":"Vacant Kingdom is a bullet hell action-RPG. Its combat takes inspiration from Japanese arcade shooters, but the story and world are structured like an action-RPG. You'll explore different locations, make friends, solve puzzles, and acquire items. Bosses will put your skills to the test, but you'll only have to defeat each one once.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704730/extras/2021-05-13_garden_2_action.png?t=1666565661\" /><br><br>In Vacant Kingdom you explore a whimsical yet desolate land and try to rally its adrift people by solving their problems. On the way you'll meet a colourful cast of characters. Like a chef who only knows one recipe, a nefarious wizard who wields the dark power of obtuse riddles, and a robot who is programmed to teach the world about insects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Gamer Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenging bullet hell gameplay in a unique action-RPG framework.<br></li><li>4-6 hours of gameplay.<br></li><li>Defeat 9 fearsome bosses.<br></li><li>3 levels of difficulty to suit beginners and veterans alike.<br></li><li>Discover a variety of equipment and weapons.<br></li><li>Explore and uncover its secrets of a haunted resort, an abandoned bathhouse, and more.<br></li><li>Solve perplexing puzzles to proceed through the world.<br></li><li>Befriend a cast of quirky characters.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704730/extras/2021-12-21_aquafloor_puzzle.gif?t=1666565661\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Games Journalist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1704730/15e9bd0727d73d0f94bf9e070616b241d822b673.jpg"},{"name":"Core Gamer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1704730/73ace264b0492a4c5838067841f0b484deb313e6.jpg"},{"name":"Orthodox Gamer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamsta